title.rendered: DASH OFFROAD Y62 Patrol Predator Front Bar Series 1-4 [Satin Black/Raw Unfinished]

content.rendered:
Dash Offroad Y62 Patrol Predator Front Bar Series 1-4 [Satin Black/Raw Unfinished]

To suit: Y62 Patrol STL, Ti, TiL – S1, 2, 3, 4*

Construction: 

  • Steel bracketry and winch cradle.
  • Aluminum 3 piece fascia

Surface: Satin black

ADR: Meets and complies with ADR

Light weight in design, aggressive approach angle, the Predator Bar is the ultimate bumper replacement for your Y62 whether you want to look good picking the kids up or out on the tracks.

PREDATOR BAR OPTIONS – BOTH INCLUDED

Option 1: Light Bar Bracket

Water proof/dust tested: IP67
Power: 100W
Size: 535mm x 40mm
Material: Aluminium housing lens
Wiring loom not included
Light bar sold seperately
Purchase the light bar here

Option 2: Accesory Bracket

Construction: Steel​
